\ Manual tdb smoke case.
\
\ Run directly from the repository root with:
\   toy --tdb --file tests\toy\manual_tdb.toy
\
\ Try `break 10`, `break tdb-inc`, `next`, `finish`, `stack`, and `bt` while
\ entering `tdb-inc` and the quotation scheduled by `times`. After its capture
\ list runs, try `locals` and `print $value`; `words` and `see tdb-inc` inspect
\ the dictionary.

'tdb-inc [ | value | $value 1 + ] def
0 2 [ tdb-inc ] times
